<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>결제 실패 | TripManager</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        .fail-box { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; }
        .error-card { background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0; text-align: left; display: inline-block; min-width: 300px; }
        .btn-group { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; }
        .btn-retry { background: #3182f6; color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="container">
        <div class="fail-box">
            <img src="/Toss_Symbol_Gray.png" width="100" alt="로고">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 20px;">결제에 실패했습니다</h2>
            <p style="color: #4e5968;">불편을 드려 죄송합니다. 아래 내용을 확인해 주세요.</p>

            <div class="error-card">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>에러 코드:</strong> <%= code %></p>
            </div>

            <div class="btn-group">
                <button onclick="history.back()" class="btn-retry">다시 시도하기</button>
                <button onclick="location.href='/'" style="border: 1px solid #d1d6db; background: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer;">홈으로 이동</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>